527:/* From the above state machine we can create the REFRESH CAS and RAS signals.  This state machine will only start running when the
528:   REFRESH_ACTIVE flag is set.   State 1 and State 2 are used for the CAS signal being low, and State 3 and State 4 for the RAS signal.
